{"tid":294132,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你經歷緊唔開心？有幾句說話俾你","createTime":"2017-06-22T16:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T15:33:41.000Z","uid":119272,"like":65,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dcd547de45883acfa6bdda9b003f8f50602a99a0","tid":294132,"uid":119272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:42:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wjw43aHMTgg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fwjw43aHMTgg&d=09rdrYZgyqH8OENbcPAzFTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c252689b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wjw43aHMTgg</a><br />\n<br />\n世界從來唔係充滿彩虹同陽光，<br />\n人生預咗有各種不同痛苦擊打你，<br />\n可能係感情、金錢、疾病、情緒，<br />\n但請你記住，<br />\n對人生既回應唔在於你出拳有幾重，<br />\n在於你可以承受到幾重既拳，再次企返起身。<br />\n<br />\n其實，係痛苦當中，你會不知不覺變得更堅強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2a339b9f6dbf98e7eea7b9a9ad4193a985b9e5","tid":294132,"uid":38077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71fc9a697f343e619d61d73e198ff972f6aa98b","tid":294132,"uid":94009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:46:10.000Z","msg":"李小龍：攻擊就係最好的防禦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc6e8c27548e1decdea4f2088a8cda51a157c7d","tid":294132,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:46:50.000Z","msg":"冷靜D照下鏡, 睇下自己個樣, 同埋睇下你本銀行存摺有幾多錢先啦<br />\n<br />\n世界好公平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果人人都心想事成<br />\n<br />\n會天下大亂<br />\n<br />\n世上總要有你D咁既廢人"},{"pid":"730ae6d49a6fafca92780217014af565005ab9bc","tid":294132,"uid":119272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冷靜D照下鏡, 睇下自己個樣, 同埋睇下你本銀行存摺有幾多錢先啦<br />\n<br />\n世界好公平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果人人都心想事成<br />\n<br />\n會天下大亂<br />\n<br />\n世上總要有你D咁既廢人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有時睇呢篇會係覺得勵志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e3061b78926e3f58effbf2b1cb512833ec735c","tid":294132,"uid":44804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"但係我唔覺得我可以企翻響身&hellip;"},{"pid":"d11b32f2e25202c6cf9084ef0a0328f67321530b","tid":294132,"uid":71742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57af0ba775e5077e7f5812358c3921645b17ac2","tid":294132,"uid":51978,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://download.ithome.com.tw/uploads/image-upload/51ef339356bdd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdownload.ithome.com.tw%2Fuploads%2Fimage-upload%2F51ef339356bdd.gif&h=e4fb98ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"565a6f303f08bf24f034ee91ba770cc9bbe27858","tid":294132,"uid":119272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:29:21.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b884eda74cd91fa276d92bd0614ff1844a14bc","tid":294132,"uid":119272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:49:14.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88490fba55c90e9a1a89fc8997922b169b4328f9","tid":294132,"uid":68589,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:10:32.000Z","msg":"我提醒自己<br />\n將來會有更大既痛苦<br />\n襯宜家仲未係最苦既時候 好好珍惜下開心既時光"},{"pid":"98c322e1cb7e17aa70325e3392836530a337937e","tid":294132,"uid":63413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:15:59.000Z","msg":"未經歷過挫折 失敗 打擊<br />\n你唔會識珍惜 識享受得來不易嘅成功<br />\n好多野都覺得係理所當然<br />\n而唔識感恩自己擁有嘅種種事物<br />\n<br />\n講到1999 唔知睇唔睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765975aeb34243ff6c5579b8106ebd08bcd93501","tid":294132,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:16:48.000Z","msg":"小見正面post咁多正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109d7409807413dcfffc9022dcf447da5cca9f9c","tid":294132,"uid":119272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小見正面post咁多正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n坊間太多心靈雞湯，其實係害人既<br />\n反而，睇清事實，一步一步默默爬返起身仲好過"},{"pid":"3a9ef2c272acedefa31887aef660d07dedfa6e4d","tid":294132,"uid":119272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我提醒自己<br />\n將來會有更大既痛苦<br />\n襯宜家仲未係最苦既時候 好好珍惜下開心既時光</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係架，而加既苦唔係最苦，怕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c1228e001f378bfc0fd9a2ba77ce2f0f76f8e3","tid":294132,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:28:57.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主<br />\n評已正"},{"pid":"5a83d80e93f0141768757de0c6f143c1a2dd6361","tid":294132,"uid":39402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:32:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小見正面post咁多正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n坊間太多心靈雞湯，其實係害人既<br />\n反而，睇清事實，一步一步默默爬返起身仲好過</blockquote><br />\n同意<br />\n我想講既係 通常連登係唔鍾意正面post 講得幾有道理都好<br />\n負面野先多人like<br />\n你依個係小數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64677275bc604a674e0d89999abfca8ac0f79f7e","tid":294132,"uid":119272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:33:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝樓主<br />\n評已正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nnot at all<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3717923fdc8c8ca15d08fdf5c4bda90f75f1cd","tid":294132,"uid":119272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:42:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未經歷過挫折 失敗 打擊<br />\n你唔會識珍惜 識享受得來不易嘅成功<br />\n好多野都覺得係理所當然<br />\n而唔識感恩自己擁有嘅種種事物<br />\n<br />\n講到1999 唔知睇唔睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明呀，人本身就係有自私貪婪之心，<br />\n想擁有更多佔有更多，<br />\n擁有緊既野就忘記咗"},{"pid":"b5125cc0e6922f374330d4e6848ed1c8876dfce5","tid":294132,"uid":65365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:10:36.000Z","msg":"I stopped being me"},{"pid":"6e730b743eef08a376613ef62b886f84617031c6","tid":294132,"uid":37629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:13:28.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主 感覺好左d <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1921a8f7a0e79dc4ad3e9b6b844a9fe6755b30","tid":294132,"uid":63413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:15:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>未經歷過挫折 失敗 打擊<br />\n你唔會識珍惜 識享受得來不易嘅成功<br />\n好多野都覺得係理所當然<br />\n而唔識感恩自己擁有嘅種種事物<br />\n<br />\n講到1999 唔知睇唔睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明呀，人本身就係有自私貪婪之心，<br />\n想擁有更多佔有更多，<br />\n擁有緊既野就忘記咗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以有時生活上好簡單嘅小事<br />\n好似 今朝返工好順利無出咩事 <br />\n準時返到工 港鐵無突然跪低 咁<br />\n你識得咁去欣賞身邊嘅事物<br />\n你嘅人生會快樂好多!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1768292/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1768292%2F&d=09rdrYZgyqH8OENbcPAzFTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=3e67b7ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1768292/</a><br />\n醫生叫森美做嘅野係好值得學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07570d73dd5421fc3b0ff55a43b3cf31de2e0c74","tid":294132,"uid":18977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:19:34.000Z","msg":"樓豬嗰幾行睇到眼濕添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 眼淺"},{"pid":"8387aa73b64337cc0beb116b2bae618cb716eb0a","tid":294132,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:00:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81bd60b7a551c79272125161200abc788f9f394f","tid":294132,"uid":119272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T08:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我無乜朋友,唉,放假都做廢青</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如試下心態轉換，好多時係自己介懷太多，<br />\n諗下呢刻有咩想做，目標，<br />\n唔理今日既效果大唔大，<br />\n起碼行動咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}